This paper involves reasoning and representation of spatial relations between objects using Answer Set Programming, which is a subfield of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). It also involves the use of constraints and preferences, which are topics in Logic (cs.LO) and Programming Languages (cs.PL). The paper also deals with consistency checking and inference, which are topics in Mathematics (cs.MA) and Databases (cs.DB).
